| DS18B20 | Arduino Uno/Nano Pin |
| VCC     | 5V                   |
| GND     | GND                  |
| Data    | D8                   |
| SCL     | A5                   |  
4.7kÎ© pull-up resistor between DATA and 5V!!    

| LCD     | Arduino Uno/Nano Pin |
| VCC     | 5V                   |
| GND     | GND                  |
| SDA     | A4                   |
| SCL     | A5                   |

| Relay   | Arduino Uno/Nano Pin |
| IN1     | D9                   |
| VCC     | 12v from battery     |
| GND     | Arduino GND          |  
| NO      | Compressor           |  
| COM     | 12v From Battery     |  

The second wire from the compressor is your ground, connect it where ever you can
